TITLE: Creating ZPA App Connector Group with Version Profile Name
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to create a ZPA App Connector Group resource using the version_profile_name attribute. It sets various properties such as name, description, location, and upgrade settings.
SOURCE: https://github.com/zscaler/terraform-provider-zpa/blob/master/docs/resources/zpa_app_connector_group.md#2025-04-22_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: terraform
CODE:
```
resource "zpa_app_connector_group" "example" {
  name                          = "Example"
  description                   = "Example"
  enabled                       = true
  city_country                  = "San Jose, CA"
  country_code                  = "US"
  latitude                      = "37.338"
  longitude                     = "-121.8863"
  location                      = "San Jose, CA, US"
  upgrade_day                   = "SUNDAY"
  upgrade_time_in_secs          = "66600"
  override_version_profile      = true
  version_profile_name          = "New Release"
  dns_query_type                = "IPV4_IPV6"
  use_in_dr_mode                = true
}
```

