TITLE: Creating REDIRECT_PREFERRED Policy Rule in Terraform
DESCRIPTION: Creates a redirection policy rule with preferred redirect action, referencing a service edge group and including client type conditions.
SOURCE: https://github.com/zscaler/terraform-provider-zpa/blob/master/docs/resources/zpa_policy_redirection_rule.md#2025-04-22_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: terraform
CODE:
```
data "zpa_service_edge_group" "this" {
    name = "Service_Edge_Group01
}

resource "zpa_policy_redirection_rule" "this" {
  name                          = "Example"
  description                   = "Example"
  action                        = "REDIRECT_PREFERRED"

  conditions {
    operator = "OR"
    operands {
      object_type = "CLIENT_TYPE"
      values      = ["zpn_client_type_branch_connector"]
    }
  }
  service_edge_groups {
    id = [ data.zpa_service_edge_group.this.id ]
  }
}
```

